        <Parent_String>alcohol (general) [300015224], organic compounds [300379624], compounds (materials) [300246922], materials by chemical form [300247255], materials by form [300014611], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
